\c 11
\s Ukuru hwaJehovha
\p
\v 1 Naizvozvo uchada Jehovha Mwari wako\x + 6.5.\x*, nekuchengeta mutemo wake nezvimiso zvake nemitongo yake nemirairo yake mazuva ese\x + Rev. 8.35. Eze. 44.16.\x*.
\v 2 Zvino zivai nhasi, nokuti handi\add tauri\add* nevana venyu vasina kuziva, uye vasina kuona kuranga kwaJehovha Mwari wenyu\x + 8.5.\x*, ukuru hwake\x + 3.24. 5.24.\x*, chanza chake chine simba, neruoko rwake rwakatandavadzwa\x + 4.34.\x*,
\v 3 nezviratidzo zvake, nezviito zvake, zvaakaita mukati meEgipita kuna Farao mambo weEgipita nekunyika yake yese\x + 6.22.\x*;
\v 4 nezvaakaita kuhondo yeEgipita, kumabhiza avo, uye kungoro dzavo; wakaita sei mvura yeGungwa Dzvuku kukukura pazviso zvavo ivo pavakateverera shure kwako; Jehovha ndokuvaparadza kusvika nhasi\x + Eki. 14.27,28. 15.9,10.\x*.
\v 5 Nezvaakaita kwamuri murenje, kusvika masvika panzvimbo ino.
\v 6 Nezvaakaita kuna Dhatani nekuna Abhiramu vanakomana vaEriabhu mwanakomana waRubheni; mashamiro akaita nyika muromo wayo, ndokuvamedza, ne\add ve\add*dzimba dzavo, nematende avo\x + Num.. 16.1,31. 27.3. Map. 106.17.\x*, nenhumbi dzose dzaiva dzavo pakati paIsraeri wese\x + Gen.. 7.4,23.\x*.
\v 7 Asi meso enyu ndiwo anoona zviito zvose zvikuru zvaJehovha zvaakaita.
\v 8 Naizvozvo munofanira kuchengeta mirairo yose yandinokuraira nhasi, kuti musimbe, mupinde, mugare nhaka yenyika iyo kwamunoyambuka kunoiita yenyu\x + Josh. 1.6,7.\x*;
\v 9 uye kuti mugorebesa mazuva panyika\x + 4.40.\x*, Jehovha yaakapikira madzibaba enyu, kupa kwavari nekuchizvarwa chavo\x + Gen.. 50.24.\x*, nyika inoyerera mukaka neuchi\x + Eki. 3.8.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Nokuti nyika kwaunoenda kunoiita yako, haina kufanana nenyika yeEgipita, kwamakabuda, kwawaidzvara mbeu dzako, uchidzidiridza netsoka dzako, semunda wemiriwo\x + Zek. 14.18.\x*.
\v 11 Asi nyika yamunoyambukira kwairi kuigara nhaka inyika yemakomo nemipata; inonwa mvura nemvura yematenga\x + 8.7.\x*;
\v 12 inyika Jehovha Mwari wako yaanochengeta; meso aJehovha Mwari wako ari pamusoro payo nguva dzese, kubva pakutanga kwegore kusvika pakupedzisira kwegore\x + 1 Madz. 9.3.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Zvino zvichaitika, kana mukateerera kwazvo kumirairo yangu yandinokurairai nhasi, kuda Jehovha Mwari wenyu, nekumushumira nemoyo wenyu wose uye nemweya wenyu wese\x + 6.5.\x*,
\v 14 kuti ndichapa mvura yenyika yenyu panguva yayo\x + Rev. 26.4. Det. 28.12.\x*, mvura yekutanga nemvura yekupedzisira, kuti uunganidze zviyo zvako, newaini yako itsva, nemafuta ako\x + Jer. 5.24. Hos. 6.3. Jow. 2.23. Jak. 5.7.\x*.
\v 15 Zvino ndichapa uswa kuzvipfuwo zvako pamafuro ako\x + Map. 104.14.\x*, uye uchadya ugoguta\x + 6.11. Jow. 2.19.\x*.
\v 16 Zvichenjererei kuti moyo yenyu irege kunyengerwa mutsauke\x + Job. 31.27. Det. 29.18.\x* ndokushumira vamwe vamwari, ndokuvanamata\x + 8.19; 30.17.\x*;
\v 17 kuti hasha dzaJehovha dzikupfutirei\x + 6.15.\x*, uye apfige matenga, kuti kusava nemvura\x + 1 Madz. 8.35. 2 Makor. 6.26. 7.13.\x*, nenyika isapa goho rayo\x + Rev. 26. 4.\x*, zvino muparare nekukurumidza kubva panyika yakanaka Jehovha yaanokupai\x + 4.26. 30.18. Josh. 23.13,15,16.\x*.
\p
\v 18 Zvino muchaisa mashoko angu awa pamoyo penyu nemumweya wenyu\x + 6.6.\x*; mugoasungira kuva chiratidzo paruoko rwenyu, kuti ave sevundanyara pakati pemeso enyu\x + 6.8. Eki. 13.9.\x*.
\v 19 Uye muchaadzidzisa vana venyu, muchitaura nezvawo kana wakagara muimba yako, uye paunofamba panzira, uye paunorara pasi, nepaunomuka\x + 4.9.\x*.
\v 20 Zvino uchaanyora pamagwatidziro eimba yako nepamasuwo ako\x + 6.9.\x*;
\v 21 kuti mazuva enyu awande, nemazuva evana venyu, panyika Jehovha yaakapikira madzibaba enyu kuvapa\x + Zvir. 4.10. 9.11. Det. 4.40. 6.2. Zvir. 3.2.\x*, semazuva ekumatenga pamusoro penyika\x + Map. 89.29.\x*.
\p
\v 22 Nokuti kana mukachengeta kwazvo mirairo iyi yose yandinokurairai, kuiita, kuda Jehovha Mwari wenyu, kufamba munzira dzake dzese\x + 6.17.\x*, uye kumunamatira\x + 10.20.\x*;
\v 23 ipapo Jehovha achadzinga ndudzi idzi dzose kubva pamberi penyu\x + 4.38.\x*, uye muchagara nhaka yemarudzi makuru uye ane simba kukupfuurai\x + 9.1.\x*.
\v 24 Nzvimbo imwe neimwe pachatsika pasi perutsoka rwenyu ichava yenyu\x + Josh. 1.3. Josh. 14.9.\x*, kubva murenje, neRebhanoni, kubva parwizi, rwizi Furati\x + Gen.. 15.18. Eki. 23.31. Num.. 34.3-12. Det. 1.7. Josh. 1.4.\x*, nekusvika kugungwa rekupedzisira, uchava muganhu wako\x + 34.2. Josh. 15.12.\x*.
\v 25 Hakuna munhu achamira pamberi penyu\x + 7.24.\x*; Jehovha Mwari wenyu achaisa kutyisa kwenyu nekuvhundusa kwenyu pamusoro penyika yose yamuchatsika pairi\x + 2.25.\x*, sezvaakataura kwamuri\x + Eki. 23.27.\x*.
\p
\v 26 Tarirai, nhasi ndinoisa pamberi penyu ropafadzo nekutukwa\x + 30.1,15,19.\x*;
\v 27 ropafadzo kana mukateerera mirairo yaJehovha Mwari wenyu yandinokurairai nhasi\x + 28.2-14.\x*;
\v 28 nekutukwa kana musingateereri mirairo yaJehovha Mwari wenyu, asi muchitsauka panzira yandinokurairai nhasi\x + 28.15-45.\x*, kutevera vamwe vamwari vamusina kuziva\x + 6.14.\x*.
\v 29 Zvino zvichaitika Jehovha Mwari wako paanokupinza panyika yaunoenda kuigara nhaka, kuti uchaisa ropafadzo pamusoro pegomo Gerizimi, nekutukwa pamusoro pegomo Ebhari\x + 27.12,13. Josh. 8.33.\x*.
\v 30 Ko haasi mhiri kwaJoridhani, shure kwenzira yekumavirazuva, munyika yeVaKenani, vagere pamapani pakatarisana neGirigari, pedo nemiouki\x + Gen.. 13.18.\x* yeMore\x + Gen.. 12.6. Vato. 7.1.\x*?
\v 31 Nokuti muchayambuka Joridhani kupinda kugara nhaka yenyika Jehovha Mwari wenyu yaanokupai; zvino muchaigara nhaka ndokugara mairi\x + 9.1.\x*.
\v 32 Chenjerai kuti muite zvimiso nemitongo zvose, zvandinoisa pamberi penyu nhasi\x + 5.32. 12.32.\x*.